findings.title: Potential unauthorized script upgrade
findings.description: The smart contract may allow an unauthorized user to upgrade the script.

findings.title: Minting of unlimited number of sundae tokens
findings.description: The owner can mint tokens after initial contract creation/deployment.

findings.title: antiBot
findings.description: Vulnerability related to anti-bot mechanism in approve, transferFrom, increaseAllowance, decreaseAllowance and transfer functions.

findings.title: onlyOwner
findings.description: The smart contract owner has elevated privileges to change trading status, bulk blacklist wallets, change transaction fees, and modify max transaction and wallet limits.
